= What needs to be calibrated?

To get good results, apart from all the parameters of the simulation, several minor stuff has to be tweaked.

1. Network topology: maybe generated or taken directly from data.
2. Metrics regarding sessions.

= What needs to be obtained from the data?
Regarding sessions:
- Is different a session initiated from a notification rather a scheduled session?
- Are creation and actions within a single session (inter session) or regarding the whole timeline (intra session)


